(62, 'Electricity Laboratory Instruments', '66', 571, NULL, NULL, 'Electricity Laboratory Instruments', NULL, '873227electrical-engineering-lab-equipment.jpg', 'electricity-laboratory-instruments', '<h2>Electricity Laboratory Instruments Manufacturers, Suppliers and Exporters</h2>\nWe manufacture the super quality of <strong>Electricity Laboratory Instruments</strong>. Our innovative brand has captured the international market.\n\nWe follow latest technology developments within the promised time frame. Excellent performance and less maintenance are the two best factors which our company follows.\n\nWe offer the best quality management system and fully customer satisfaction. Our offered range comprises of Bicycle Dynamo Assembly, Capacitance Box, Coil High Inductance, Decade Capacitance Box and Demonstration, Electric Bell and Double C Core And Clip etc. We are also available at Facebook, Twitter as well as Google+.', 'Electricity Laboratory Instruments', 'Electricity laboratory instruments leading manufacturers, supplier and exporters in India. Get ISO certified laboratory equipment contact us for quote', 'Electricity Laboratory Instruments Manufacturer and Suppler In India', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:26', '2021-11-11 13:10:56', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
(63, 'Biology Lab Equipment', '567', NULL, NULL, 0, 'Biology Lab Equipment', NULL, '964996bio.gif', 'biology-lab-equipment', '<h2 style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Biology Lab Equipment Manufacturer and Supplier in Malaysia</h2><p class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Atico Scientific is an ISO-certified company, has been manufacturing, supplying, and exporting biology lab equipment to high-end laboratories for decades. We are a top biology lab equipment manufacturer in Malaysia, building the pillars of biological research by providing precision-crafted lab equipment that is best suited for all levels of academic and research laboratories in schools, colleges, universities, and research institutions. Each piece of lab equipment allows students to perform accurate experiments and gain practical experience that supports superior, in-depth science knowledge.</p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">We are a renowned biology lab equipment supplier in Malaysia. We know how crucial it is to have quality and precision biology lab equipment in biostudies. We offer a high-quality product range that varies from basic to sophisticated biology laboratory equipment. We believe in product reliability, and everything we deal in is manufactured as per international standards of accuracy and safety. Being a global biology lab equipment exporter in Malaysia, we are happy to export our products to promote long-term performance and build healthy business relationships.</p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Being able to design the equipment to suit the specific curriculum and research needs of schools is why we are the best biology lab equipment manufacturer in Malaysia, supplier, and exporter, and an exceptional business partner for decades.</p>', 'Biology Lab Equipment, Biology Lab Equipment Manufacturer, Biology Lab Equipment Supplier, Biology Lab Equipment Exporter', 'Leading Biology Lab Equipment Manufacturer, Supplier & Exporter in Malaysia. Durable instruments for schools, colleges & research labs. Fast global delivery.', 'Biology Lab Equipment Manufacturers and Supplier in Malaysia', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:26', '2025-11-21 12:18:49', NULL, NULL, 2, NULL),
(64, 'Educational Charts', '63', 569, 567, NULL, 'Educational Charts', NULL, '263176edu_chart.jpg', 'educational-charts', 'A chart is a symbolic&nbsp;representation&nbsp;of&nbsp;data or information according to some&nbsp;visualization&nbsp;technique. The information in a chart is represented graphically, it is also known as a graph. <strong>Educational Charts</strong> are often used to ease understanding of large quantities of data because humans are generally able to understand meaning from pictures quicker than from text. In the <b>Educational Lab Equipments</b> department, charts are used in <b><a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/category/biology-lab-equipment\" title=\"\" target=\"\">biological labs</a></b> as well as pharmacy, chemistry, physical and mathematical labs. Charts are often playing its vital role in the field of mechanical, electronic, electrical engineering.\n<h2>Educational Charts Manufacturer, Supplier, and Exporter</h2>\nAt Atico Export, the teams of highly skilled experts manufacture charts and diagrams to help students in their education and make their future bright by polishing their skills in any field. The&nbsp;<b>Educational Lab Instruments</b> and other lab<b>&nbsp;</b>products we manufacturing are Porifera Coelenterata Platyhelminthes, Human Reproduction and Physiology, General Science Charts (Polyart), Botany Charts, Policharts, Bio Periodic Tables Polyart, Special Human Physiology Charts in their registered firm. We supply these charts in the national and international market for the last couple of years. We also build charts on special offers; please have a look at products we create here:', 'Educational Charts', 'We are Educational Charts Manufacturers, Suppliers and Exporters that are used for educational purposes to understand the concepts easily.', 'Educational Charts Manufacturers, Suppliers and Exporters', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:26', '2021-11-11 13:39:52', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
(65, 'Hospital Utensils and Hollowares', '0', NULL, NULL, 0, 'Hospital utensils and hollowares', NULL, '165356hospital-holloware-500x500.jpg', 'hospital-utensils-and-hollowares', 'We are suppliers of Hospitals Utensils and Hollowares. The entire range of Hospital Utensils is available here. You can join us social media like facebook, twitter as well as Google+.', 'Hospital utensils and hollowares', 'Hospital utensils and hollowares leading manufacturers, supplier and exporters in India. Get ISO certified laboratory equipment contact us for quote', 'Hospital Utensils and Hollowares Manufacturer and Suppler In India', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:26', '2019-10-14 19:25:36', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
(66, 'Physics Lab Equipment Manufacturer', '567', NULL, NULL, 0, 'Physics lab equipment', NULL, '825510physics lab equipment aticoscientific.png', 'physics-lab-equipment', '<h2><font color=\"#172b4d\" face=\"Open Sans, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Physics Lab Equipment Manufacturer in Malaysia</span></font></h2><div><p class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Atico Scientific is the leading <a href=\"https://www.aticoindia.com/category/physics-lab-equipment\" title=\"\" target=\"\">physics lab equipment manufacturer</a> in Malaysia, known as a trusted supplier and exporter of high-quality physics lab instruments Our equipment is engineered for schools, colleges, universities, technical institutes, government labs, and research organizations that demand reliable results and long-term product life rather than cheap disposable tools.</p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: