hat you need, we offer complete customization based on your required specifications.</p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; min-height: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">With a strong global distribution network, fast delivery across Malaysia and international markets, as well as dedicated technical support, we\'ve established long-term partnerships with thousands of institutions across the world. We keep affordability in focus without compromising on accuracy to make our solutions perfect for today\'s science learning environment.</p></div>', 'Physics lab equipment manufacturer, Physics lab equipment supplier', 'Leading Physics Lab Equipment Manufacturer, Supplier & Exporter in Malaysia. High-precision instruments for schools, colleges & research labs. Global delivery.', 'Physics Lab Equipment Manufacturer and Suppliers in Malaysia', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:26', '2025-11-20 06:50:50', NULL, NULL, 2, NULL),
