(80, 'Aggregate Testing Equipment', '79', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'aggregate testing equipment manufacturers', NULL, '856676aggregate-impact-testing-machine-500x500.jpg', 'aggregate-testing-equipment', '<div><h2><strong>Aggregate Testing Equipment</strong></h2><br></div><strong>Aggregate Testing Equipment</strong> is part of <a href=\"https://www.aticoexport.com/product_category/civil-engineering-instruments\">Civil Engineering Instruments</a>. We are manufacturer and supplier of <a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/category/aggregate-testing-equipment\" title=\"aggregate testing equipment manufacturers\" target=\"\"><i><strong>Aggregate Testing Equipment</strong> </i></a>in worldwide range. Testing instruments are required to be of best quality as it is essential to get the predictable result accurately. So, we made all testing equipments in an innovative way and fully trusted to provide accurate results.\nWe fabricate the instruments using the latest tools and based on the ideas of skilled professionals. Testing Equipments are made by using industrial quality components. We fulfill the client specified requirements.<div><br></div><div>Ask for details via email and chat support, drop your requirements, and message our reprehensive connect in 24 hours with details information! We believe in customer satisfaction in all aspects. Our team is committed to providing high-quality laboratory equipment at attractive prices!&nbsp;<br></div>', 'aggregate testing equipment manufacturers', 'Aggregate Testing Equipment manufacturer, suppliers and exporters in India. Atico Leading engineering lab equipments and accessories list, suppliers at best prices! Ask details', 'Aggregate Testing Equipment Manufacturer and Suppliers in India', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:27', '2022-05-13 16:10:06', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
(81, 'Bitumen Testing Equipment', '79', NULL, NULL, 0, 'Bitumen Testing Equipment', NULL, '327390bitumen-testing-equipment-500x500.jpg', 'bitumen-testing-equipment', '<b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\" calibri\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:=\"\" minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa\"=\"\"><h2>Bitumen\nTesting Equipment Manufacturers, Suppliers, and Exporters</h2></span></b><br>', 'Bitumen Testing Equipment', 'We have an extensive range of Bitumen Testing Equipment. Our Manufacturer, Supplier and Exporter provide high quality lab apparatus in many companies.', 'Bitumen Testing Equipment Manufacturer, Supplier and Exporter', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:27', '2021-01-06 15:28:24', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
(82, 'Cement Testing Equipment', '79', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Cement Testing Equipment', NULL, '291460cement-testing-equipment-500x500.jpg', 'cement-testing-equipment', '<h2>Cement Testing Equipment Manufacturer, Supplier, and Exporter</h2><div><div>Atico India stands as a distinguished cement testing laboratory equipment manufacturer, supplier, and exporter in India. Our commitment to excellence is reflected in the impeccable quality and precision of our cement testing instruments, crafted using superior raw materials under the vigilant supervision of our experienced laboratory experts.</div><div><br></div><div>Renowned as the foremost cement testing laboratory equipment supplier, our products have found prominence in engineering colleges, universities, research and testing laboratories, vocational training centers, government projects, and civil organizations globally. Our range of cement testing instruments encompasses a diverse array of essential tools, ensuring comprehensive coverage for all testing and experimentation needs.</div><div><br></div><div>Choose Atico India as your trusted partner in cement testing equipment. Our dedication to quality and precision has made us the preferred supplier for prestigious institutions and projects worldwide. Elevate your cement testing processes with our cutting-edge laboratory instruments and experience the difference in performance and results.</div></div>', 'Cement Testing Equipment', 'Atico India is renowned Cement Testing Equipment manufacturers, suppliers and exporters from India. Contact us today for bulk order.', 'Cement Testing Equipment Manufacturer, Supplier and Exporter', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:27', '2024-01-31 17:07:49', NULL, NULL, 2, NULL),
(83, 'Compression Testing Equipment', '79', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Compression Testing Equipment', NULL, '442332semi-automatic-digital-compression-testing-machine-500x500.jpg', 'compression-testing-equipment', '<div><h2 style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><b>Atico&nbsp;Compression Testing Equipment&nbsp;</b></h2></div><div><br></div><font size=\"3\">At Atico Lab Export, we take quality, durability and usability very serious. <b style=\"\"><a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/category/compression-testing-equipment\" title=\"Compression Testing Equipment Manufacturers\" target=\"\">Compression testing equipment</a> </b>is used to test the limit of any material or to set the limits which imply the ability of a material to resist that compression/ pressure. This testing is utilized to test the compressive power or pulverize obstruction of any material. It additionally uncovers the capacity of a material to recuperate after use of a predetermined compressive for a predefined timeframe. By utilizing materials testing hardware, you can build up the most extreme pressure a material can withstand over a period of time under a load that can either be consistent or dynamic.<br></font><br><h2><h3><strong>Importance of pressure/ compression test:</strong></h3><strong><br></strong></h2><font size=\"3\">\nPressure tests decide how a material or a made item responds when it is packed, smashed or squashed under a compressive load. Pressure tests can be performed during the design process or manufacturing or when the quality check is taking place. The <u style=\"\">compression testing instrument</u> makes the material free form danger. Testing is very important before the utilization of the material. If the material would not go under a compression test then there is a huge possibility of sudden accidents.\n\n<b style=\"\">Compression testing equipment</b></font><font size=\"3\" style=\"\"><b> is used in different industries some of them are:</b><br></font><br>\n<ul>\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><font size=\"3\">Plastic, Tin industry</font></span></li>\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><font size=\"3\">Safety, fitness and medical industry</font></span></li>\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><font size=\"3\">Aerospace and Automobile industry</font></span></li>\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><font size=\"3\">brick industry…..and hundred other industry</font></span></li>\n</ul>\n<font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Compression testing is used for determining to be many factors such as</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Quality, Uniformity and Design process</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reduce danger and improve the quality to achieve the company’s goal</span>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Compression testing equipment, some of them are:</span>\n</font><ul>\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><font size=\"3\">Triaxial compression testing machine</font></span></li>\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><font size=\"3\">Unconfined compression testing machine</font></span></li>\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><font size=\"3\">Compression testing machine ( plate model)</font></span></li>\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><font size=\"3\">Compression testing machine (2 pillars type)</font><br><br></span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2></h2>\n<h2><h2><b>Atico Compression Testing Equipment Manufacturers and Suppliers: &nbsp;</b></h2><b>&nbsp;&nbsp;</b></h2><font size=\"3\">\nATICO Lab Export came in existence in 1954, is an industry of manufacturing and supplying of the <a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/\" title=\"Science Lab Equipment\" target=\"\" style=\"\"><b>science lab equipments</b></a> and instruments. Our company deals with superior and high state-of-art technology and infrastructure to manufacture the quality product as per ISO certifications. Our team of engineers take after strict quality confirmation conventions implementing investigation of all items at each phase of assembling gear. This ensures that the final product that will be of utmost quality meeting and as per the customer’s satisfaction. And to be known as the best&nbsp;<b>Compression testing equipment</b>&nbsp;manufacturer, exporter and supplied by the different dealer</font>', 'Compression Testing Equipment', 'Compression Testing Equipment & OEM manufacturers, suppliers and exporters in India. Atico leading engineering lab equipment and accessories suppliers offer best prices! Ask details', 'Compression Testing Equipment Manufacturers and Suppliers in India', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:27', '2022-05-13 18:14:43', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
(84, 'Construction Equipment', '79', NULL, NULL, 0, 'Construction Equipment', NULL, '509526construction-hardware-industrial-tools-flat-vector-20489881.jpg', 'construction-equipment', '<b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\" calibri\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:=\"\" minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa\"=\"\"><h2>Construction\nEquipment Manufacturer, Supplier, and Exporter</h2></span></b><div><br></div><div>Atico is a&nbsp;<strong>Heavy Construction Equipment Machinery Trader Parts Distributors</strong> <strong>and Manufacturers</strong>. We are a tremendous firm among traders and distributors of the World. We are well known for quality plus quantity thing. More than thirty countries are using our products and give positive reviews that prove the standard of <a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/category/laboratory-instruments\" title=\"\" target=\"\"><b>Laboratory Instruments</b></a> and their related services.\n\nA wide range of category products is available for exporting and much more for manufacturing also. Some of them are listed as furnished: It consists of Concrete Mixer, Weigh Batcher, Hycon 1000q Tipper, Mini Mobile Batching Plant and so further of same category standard with their specifications.\n\nAtico Export is the world’s famous brand in the world of manufacturing and supplying goods. Grasp more listing supplies by following the given page describing instruments and their descriptions.</div>', 'Construction Equipment', 'Atico Lab Export manufacture and supply heavy Construction Equipment machines such as Concrete Mixer, Weigh Batcher, and Mini Mobile Batching Plant etc.', 'Construction Equipment Manufacturer, Supplier and Exporter', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:27', '2021-01-06 13:52:23', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL);
