(86, 'Soil Testing Equipment', '79', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Soil Testing Equipment', NULL, '364807liquid_limit_cone_penetrometer_automatic01-removebg-preview.png', 'soil-testing-equipment', '<h2>Soil Testing Equipment Manufacturer, Supplier &amp; Exporter</h2><div><br></div>\nATICO Exports is a well-established name in the manufacturing of Laboratory Testing Instruments and one of the largest<strong> Soil Testing Equipment Manufacturer, Supplier and Exporter in India</strong>. Confirming to the international standards, we are a trusted Indian brand that is the precisely fabricated range in all sorts of scientific lab testing instruments, especially Soil Testing instruments. Atico Export is backed by the most experienced and proficient engineers thereby manufacturing world-class quality, reliable and affordable products.\n\nStringent national, as well as International Quality Standards, have generated quality assurance awareness among the manufacturers and suppliers as well as customers. This very source also helps and motivates us to design and develop flawlessly performing high quality, high standards, and highly reliable soil testing Instruments.<div><br><h2>High-Quality Soil Testing Laboratory Equipment</h2><div><br></div>\nAtico Export is a prominent <strong>Soil Testing Equipment supplier </strong>throughout the country. We cover a wide array of <strong>Soil <a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/category/testing-lab-machines\" title=\"\" target=\"\">Testing Lab Equipment</a></strong> to accomplish various testing needs including sampling, classification, and evaluation of any material ranging from soil, sand, clay, gravel, or rock for road and bridge construction, excavations, foundations, and earthworks. We have a plethora of soil testing instruments varying from equipment used to examine soil samples in the laboratory to in-situ testing equipment at construction sites. Such instruments predict the mechanical behavior of soil which is the very base of any construction such as buildings, roads, bridges, or other infrastructure.\n\nThe selection of construction materials, design parameters, and foundation systems have directly connected to the characteristics of soil property. Any construction made under stringent quality assurance supervision has always resulted in satisfactory outcomes. Therefore Soil and Geotechnical investigation is strongly recommended to assure a rigid and durable structure constructed above the soil. These two investigations play a vital role in determining the physical properties of soil and also the rocks beneath.\n\nThe instruments made by ATICO Export, a leading <strong>Soil testing Instruments exporter</strong>, help in mechanical soil property evaluation, Soil classification, collection of samples as well as testing of completed road base and sub-base on site. Each and every soil testing product manufactured by our company adheres to the International Quality standards.\n\nWe have a significant contribution in designing and constructing soil testing instruments that perform typical tests to determine moisture content, characteristics at different moisture content, grain size analysis. Other testing instruments include equipment used to perform permeability, compaction density, triaxial shear, direct shear, unconfined compressive strength tests, etc.\n\nWe strive to provide best class soil testing instruments to our customers. Our motive is to design and develop precise and accurate testing equipments.</div>', 'Soil Testing Equipment', 'We manufacture and export a complete range of Soil Testing for construction industries. Contact to our suppliers online to get the material testing instruments.', 'Soil Testing Equipment Manufacturer, Supplier and Exporter', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:27', '2023-07-07 16:19:49', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
(87, 'Survey Instruments', '79', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Survey Equipments', NULL, '832622survey-instruments-500x500.jpg', 'survey-instruments', '<h2>Survey Equipments<br><br></h2>\nWe are <b>manufacturer and supplier of Survey Instruments</b> in domestic as well as international market. We have captured the market since 1954 and growing continuously since its inception.\nWe always satisfy our customers by providing high-quality materials and also based on latest technology. We are available on Facebook, Twitter as well as Google+. Our range of <b>Survey Instruments</b> includes <i>Digital Theodolite, Total Station, Auto Level, Digital Level, Dumpy Level, Laser Distance Meter, Pedometer, Total Station, Total Station Laser and many others</i>.', 'Survey Equipments', 'Survey Equipments manufacturers, suppliers and exporters in India. Leading ISO cerified engineering lab equipment suppliers in India.', 'Survey Equipments Manufacturers and Suppliers in India', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:27', '2022-05-13 14:33:04', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
