(90, 'Robotic Kits Trainers, Manufacturer, Supplier & Exporter', '73', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Robotic Kits Trainers', NULL, '9318996-Axis-Robot-ARM-Trainer.jpg', 'robotic-kits-trainers', '<div><h2><font size=\"5\">Robotic Kits Trainers</font></h2></div><div><br></div><div>Make your own robot with superior class constituents. Atico provide their consumers a high quality category product of <strong>Robotic Kits Trainers</strong>. We are spreading our business in whole world day by day. We have already gain name in manufacturing and exporting of Lab instruments in India as well as abroad.\n\nThere are many educational trainers are provided by us. <br></div><div><br></div><div>Some of these are furnished as follows: Infrared Remote control kits- Titan Tank, Escape Robot Kit (Infrared Sensor), Scarab Robot Kit (Sound Sensor), Hexapod Monster, Turning Frog (Sound Sensor), Sound Reversing Car, Line Tracking Mouse, Robotic Arm, and 6-axis Robotic Trainer etc.\n\nWe grasp the feedback of clients so that if any issue or mishandling in supplying of good occurred then our team will improve the maintenance next time. We give warranty of products also. We are concerning with consumers satisfaction with the material we made or supplied. Explore more about equipment and their specification by scrolling down the page.</div>', 'Robotic Kits Trainers', 'Atico Robotic Kits Trainers manufacturers, suppliers and exporters India. High quality educational trainers kits and equipments suppliers in India. Get details now!', 'Robotic Kits Trainers Manufacturers, Suppliers and Exporters in India', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:27', '2022-05-12 19:49:57', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
