(95, 'Concrete Testing Equipment', '79', NULL, NULL, 0, 'Concrete Lab Testing Equipment', NULL, '279506concrete-testing-equipment-500x500.jpg', 'concrete-testing-equipment', '<div><h2 style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><b></b></h2><h2><b>Concrete</b>&nbsp;<b>Testing</b>&nbsp;<b>Equipments</b>&nbsp;<b>Manufacturers and Suppliers</b></h2></div><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><div><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></div>An eminent </span><b>Concrete Testing Equipments manufacturer, supplier, and exporter </b>company in India<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, </span><a href=\"https://www.aticoexport.com\"><b>ATICO Export</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, is one among the best in India. We offer all kinds of <strong>C</strong></span><strong>oncrete </strong><b>Testing Equipment</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;utilized for onsite as well as in laboratory testing of concrete.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Concrete comprises binding material and aggregates. The binding material usually is a combination of cement and water. Aggregates used can be anything from rock, sand to gravel. So, fine or coarse aggregates combined together with water and binding material (Portland cement) makes concrete. This particular mixture is used for construction purposes. To determine and establish the quality, strength, and durability of concrete used on site, it has to undergo various quality tests. As concrete is used to build all giant and small structures, it is vital to perform concrete testing to ensure the resilience and strength of the building or structure constructed.</span><div><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Concrete materials testing can be divided into two categories: On-site or field testing and laboratory testing. These two primary categories are then sub-divided into various other concrete testing options naming concrete slump testing, air content testing, destructive concrete testing, compressive strength testing, tensile or flexural concrete testing, etc.</span>\n<h2><b></b></h2><h3><b>Best&nbsp;Concrete</b>&nbsp;<b>Testing</b>&nbsp;<b>Equipments</b>&nbsp;<b>Exporters</b></h3>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ATICO Exports, a giant among </span><b>Concrete Testing Equipments Supplier</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, caters to all the fresh and in-place concrete structures testing requirements. Known worldwide for our quality, we offer a complete section of concrete testing equipment as per International and national standards. We are also one of the best </span><b>Concrete</b> <b>Testing</b> <b>Equipments</b> <b>Exporters</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> in the world, making the vast and compound relationship among consumers in India as well as Abroad.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In order to contrive specific issues encountered on the project, various testing equipment has been made and can be optimized as per the specific situation. The few are named here Volume Change Apparatus, Vibrating Table, Vee Bee Consistometer, Concrete Vibrator Machine With Nozzle, Tile Flexural Testing Machine, Point Load Index Tester, Concrete Vibrator, Needle Vibrator, O Funnel Apparatus, Fill Box For Scc Test, Cube Mould, Hydraulic Jack, Cylindrical Moulds, Extensometer, Concrete thermometer, Lateral Extensometer, J Ring Apparatus, Concrete Permeability Apparatus, Concrete Test Hammer and so many of the same sort of Instruments.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our team aspires to achieve Customer Satisfaction by offering quality products along with convenient delivery. If you are interested to buy the latest range of branded products, you can go through our site or simply scroll the page down and check the specification of the particular purchase you want.</span></div>', 'Concrete Lab Testing Equipment', 'Our Manufacturer and Supplier provide extensive range of Concrete Lab Testing Equipment and they also export the instruments globally.', 'Concrete Lab Testing Equipment Manufacturer and Supplier', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:27', '2021-01-06 12:47:50', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
