(100, 'Measuring Instruments ', '0', NULL, NULL, 0, 'Measuring Instruments ', NULL, 'Digital-Insulation-Tester-1-300x300.jpg', 'measuring-instruments', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ATICO Export is a leading <strong>M</strong></span><b>easuring Equipment Manufacturer, Supplier and Exporter in India</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. We are the world’s top supplier of scientific lab instruments offering solutions and services to industrial and educational sector since inception. We manufacture, supply and export a vast array of lab equipment of high precision and un-doubting quality. We aim to achieve our vision through fair business ethics and technological expertise. We aspire to be a globally recognized corporation providing the best scientific equipment which is reliable, precise and accurate, available worldwide at affordable prices. </span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ATICO Export’s wide range of product offerings includes all scientific laboratory equipment including measuring equipment used in various research and testing laboratories. We are</span><b> Measuring Equipment Supplier</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. We are the renowned supplier of all types of measuring instruments developed in accordance with latest and advanced technology. Backed by a team of professional and highly skilled best-in-class people, we have marked our presence in the global market. Our professionals make use of best quality raw material and resources to manufacture precision measuring instruments and gauges. </span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>ATICO Export</strong> is a market leader in manufacturing equipment offering portable and stationary measurement solutions. We offer measuring equipment, services and solutions for industrial and research processes for measuring flow level, fill level, pressure, temperature and analytics. Our measuring equipment are being used for various industries and educational segments for measurement, calibration and testing. Our customers deal in varied industries such as electronics, chemical, energy and power stations, metal, food-stuffs, life sciences, oil and gas, and water, waste material management and many more. Some of our measuring products are Micrometer, Vernier Caliper, Dial Caliper, Height Gauge, Surface Plate, Dial Test Indicator, Dial Thickness Gauge, Bore Gauge, Dial Indicator, Dial Indicator Stand, Linear Gauge, Gauge Block, Height Master, Electric Gauges Contractor, Toolmakers Microscope Profile Projector, Coordinate Measuring Machine, Linear Scale etc.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Leveraging on our experience, we have placed ourselves in the upper echelons of the scientific lab manufacturing industry. We are the top <strong>M</strong></span><b>easurement Equipment Exporter</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> in the world. We have never compromised on quality. Each and every instrument is highly précised and accurate and is very suitable for measuring, testing, analyzing and controlling data. We work with die-hard determination and incessant inspiration, thereby maintaining a top position in the global market gaining trustworthy customer-base. If you are looking for any scientific lab equipment please go through our company profile and products and give us the opportunity to serve.</span>', 'Measuring Instruments ', 'Measuring instruments  leading manufacturers, supplier and exporters in India. Get ISO certified laboratory equipment contact us for quote', 'Measuring Instruments  Manufacturer and Supplier In India', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:27', '2019-10-11 16:29:25', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
