(127, 'Bread Board Trainers', '73', 566, NULL, NULL, 'Bread Board Trainers kit, Bread Board Trainers', NULL, '760491power-project-board_477932.jpg', 'bread-board-trainers', '<h2><strong>Board Trainers&nbsp;Manufacturer, Supplier &amp; Exporter<br><br></strong></h2>\nAtico Export is the best Bread <strong>Board Trainers&nbsp;Manufacturer, Exporter and Suppliers in India</strong>. For all logical lab hardware we are the significant provider from over 60 years. A&nbsp;breadboard&nbsp;is a piece of polished wood used for slicing bread. This is become extremely popular with students and in technological education, because it is easy to use for creating experimenting with circuit design. A variety of electronic and electrical systems may be prototyped by using breadboards, from small analog and digital circuits to complete CPUs.\n<br><br>Atico Export is Manufacturer and exporter of D S P Trainer, Digital Communication Trainer, <strong>Bread Board Trainer</strong> and supplies it in over than 30 countries. The experienced technical team work hard to meet requirements of the clients by providing them a huge range of lab instruments including: Digital Trainer Board, Power Electronics Lab, Digital Trainer, Digital- Analog Lab, Digital Lab, Power Project Board, Logic Lab, Digital Lab Station, Digital Logic Trainer / Logic Trainer Board, Digital Electronic Trainer, Bread Board Circuit Lab, Logic Gates Circuit Trainer, Digital Logic Trainer (TTL) Logic Trainer Board and Electricity Lab etc.\n\nNeed more information OR If you wish to know the costs of our products, then&nbsp;fill this short form&nbsp;and we’ll get in touch with you soon!<div><br></div><div>Ask for details via email and chat support, drop your requirements, and message our reprehensive connect in 24 hours with details information! We believe in customer satisfaction in all aspects. Our team is committed to providing high-quality laboratory equipment at attractive prices!&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></div>', 'Bread Board Trainers kit, Bread Board Trainers', 'Bread Board Trainers kit manufacturer, suppliers and exporters in India. Atico Leading engineering lab equipments and accessories list, suppliers at best prices! Ask details', 'Bread Board Trainers Kit Manufacturers and Suppliers in India', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:28', '2022-05-13 16:18:16', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
(128, 'Communication Trainers', '73', 566, NULL, 0, 'Communication Trainers', NULL, '711560untitled-1-250x250.jpg', 'communication-trainers', 'Grab huge range of all categories of Analog and Digital Communication Lab Trainers equipment and instruments at reasonable price from us. We are keen and fervent manufacturers and suppliers of Laboratory products. We are supplying our goods all around the world which consists more than 30 countries.\n<h2>Communication Trainers Manufacturer, Supplier and Exporter</h2>\nThe equipment, we built is always of high quality fresh constituents. These sort of category comprises so many trainers kit. Some of them are like optical Fibers Communication Trainer, Color Television Trainer, Transmission Line Trainer, Microwave Communication Trainer, Frequency Modulation &amp; Demodulation, Pulse Position Modulation &amp; Demodulation, Amplitude Modulation &amp; Demodulation and further more of same class.\n\nAtico Export is a famous brand in importing and exporting, who is spreading its business internationally and growing day by day. We made products to give a practical view of study between students, trainers and institutions. Grasp detailed view of each equipment by scrolling down the page.', 'Communication Trainers', 'Communication trainers leading manufacturers, supplier and exporters in India. Get ISO certified laboratory equipment contact us for quote', 'Communication Trainers Manufacturer and Supplier In India', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:28', '2021-05-05 16:47:18', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
(129, 'Consumer Electronics Trainers', '73', 566, NULL, 0, 'Consumer Electronics Trainers', NULL, '659937download (11).jpg', 'consumer-electronics-trainers', '<div><b><h2>High-Quality&nbsp;Consumer Electronics Trainers Manufacturer, Supplier, Exporter</h2></b></div><strong><div><strong><br></strong></div>Consumer Electronics Trainers</strong> are basically the electronics or digital devices or equipment that are used in our day today life and often available in our houses like CD/VCD Player, Colour TV, Washing Machine, Mobile Phone, FM Radio, Refrigeration system. This discrete device or physical entity in an electronic system used is mainly used for entertainment purposes.\n\nMain consumer electronics products that are a manufacturer in our firm are Load Cell Demonstrator, EPABX Trainer, Stereo Tape Recorder Trainer, SMD Technology Kit, ATM Demonstrator, RFID Trainer, Frequency Counter Trainer, UPS Trainer, SMPS Trainer, Power Supply Trainer, Oscilloscope Demonstrator Trainer, Trainer, Multimedia Computer Trainer, Trainer, PA ( Public Address ) System Trainer, Telephone Trainer, Facsimile Dynamic Demonstrator, etc. Atico team serves these instruments in the national and international science market.\n\nNeed more details on consumer electronic products and their cost? Then contact us anytime.', 'Consumer Electronics Trainers', 'Manufacturer, Supplier, Exporter at Atico Lab Export offer high quality Consumer Electronics Trainers and other lab apparatus.', 'Consumer Electronics Trainers Manufacturer, Supplier, Exporter', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:28', '2021-05-05 16:48:51', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
(131, 'Technical Educational Lab Equipment', '349', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Technical Educational Lab Equipment', NULL, '524405technical-education-lab-equipments-500x500.jpg', 'technical-educational-lab-equipment', '<div bis_skin_checked=\"1\">As a leading technical education equipment manufacturer and supplier in the industry, we take pride in providing top-quality equipment that empowers students and educators in their pursuit of knowledge and practical skills.</div><div bis_skin_checked=\"1\"><br></div><div bis_skin_checked=\"1\">Our commitment to excellence is evident in every piece of technical educational equipment we manufacture. With meticulous attention to detail and adherence to industry standards, we ensure that our products meet the highest levels of quality and functionality.</div><div bis_skin_checked=\"1\"><br></div><div bis_skin_checked=\"1\">Our extensive range of technical education equipment covers a wide array of disciplines, including engineering, electronics, robotics, computer science, and more. From basic lab tools to advanced training systems, we offer comprehensive solutions to meet the needs of educational institutions, vocational training centers, and technical workshops.<br></div>', 'Research Lab glassware equipment', 'Technical Educational Equipment manufacturer, and supplier. We are leading Technical Educational Equipment supplier in Malaysia, Bangladesh, Singapore, Dubai, Bhutan, Kuwait', 'Technical Educational Equipment Manufacturer, Supplier, and Exporter', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:28', '2023-06-14 10:43:10', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
