(157, 'Research Microscopes', '153', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Research Microscopes', NULL, '302705dissection-500x500.jpg', 'research-microscopes', '<h2><b>Research Microscopes Manufacturers</b></h2><p><br></p><p>We are manufacturer and supplier of <strong>Research Microscopes</strong>. We acquire the brand quality based on our high tech tools and technology. We work for Client satisfaction of India as well as 30 other worldwide countries.</p>\n<p>We provide all types of <strong>Lab Microscopes</strong> to all big industries, High- school and colleges <a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/product/student-stereo-microscope\" title=\"student microscope\" target=\"\"><b>student microscope</b></a>. Atico Export has achieved a good place at international level. </p><p><br></p>\n<p>If you are looking for a good quality product then Atico is the brand which can fulfill your required conditions like less maintenance and repairing, high quality, easy installation, and other best services. </p><p><br></p><p>Ask for details via email and chat support, drop your requirements, and message our reprehensive connect in 24 hours with details information! We believe in customer satisfaction in all aspects. Our team is committed to providing high-quality laboratory equipment at attractive prices!&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p><p>\n</p><p><br></p>', 'Research Microscopes', 'Research Microscopes manufacturers, suppliers and exporters in India. Atico leading Lab Microscopes and accessories suppliers offer best prices! Ask details', 'Research Microscopes Manufacturers, Suppliers and Exporters in India', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:30', '2022-05-13 17:18:37', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
(158, 'Projection Microscope', '153', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Projection Microscope, accessories', NULL, '383279projection-microscope-500x500.jpg', 'projection-microscope', '<h2>Projection Microscope at Best Prices in India</h2><p><br></p><p>If you are looking for superior quality then Atico India can end your search. Atico India is the biggest&nbsp;<strong>manufacturer and Supplier of Projection Microscope</strong>. </p> \n<p>We provide our school science lab supplies in 30 worldwide countries. Quality matters so that we make a product that provides complete satisfaction. </p><p><br></p><p>With our Projection Microscope, you can effortlessly explore the intricate details of microscopic samples and share them with larger audiences. The advanced projection feature allows you to project the microscopic image onto a screen or wall, enabling a clear and immersive visual experience for a group of viewers. This makes it an ideal choice for classroom lectures, scientific presentations, and collaborative discussions.<br></p><p><br></p>    \n<p>We have the entire range of <strong>Lab Microscopes</strong> which are supplied to all colleges, high schools,  IITs, and NITs. We manufacture products based on high-tech tools and technology.</p>', 'Projection Microscope, accessories', 'Projection microscope manufacturers, suppliers and exporters. Leading lab microscope and accessories supplier in India. Projection microscope at best prices!', 'Projection Microscope Manufacturers and Suppliers in India', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:30', '2023-06-02 11:26:47', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
(159, 'Microscope', '153', NULL, NULL, 0, 'Microscope', NULL, '240487plastic-surgery-equipment-names-of-orthopedic-surgical.jpg_350x350.jpg', 'microscope', '<h2>Microscope Manufacturers, Suppliers and Exporters</h2><br>', 'Microscope', 'Atico Lab Export manufacture, supply and exports various types of microscope accessories for schools, colleges, hospitals and research laboratories.', 'Microscope Manufacturers, Suppliers and Exporters', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:30', '2021-01-06 13:40:06', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
(160, 'Metallurgical Microscope', '153', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Metallurgical Microscope', NULL, '839980Product_Mx_Img_584499083_MT03020313-1-02-F_420x.png', 'metallurgical-microscope', '<h2>Metallurgical Microscope</h2><p><br></p><p>We are <strong>manufacturer and supplier of Metallurgical Microscope</strong>. We are playing a key role  in the manufacturing of <strong><a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/\" title=\"Scientific Lab Instruments manufacturers in India\" target=\"\"><i>Scientific Lab Instruments</i></a><strong>.</strong></strong></p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: bold;\">We are suppliers of <strong><a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/category/chemistry-lab-equipment\" title=\"Chemistry Lab Equipment\" target=\"\">Laboratory Instruments</a></strong> worldwide. In international market, Atico has become the most popular brand. We always focus on client satisfaction. Our skilled team members test each and every product so that clients can use it easily and free from any stake.</p>\n<p style=\"\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Quality is an utmost factor for us so clients have full faith in our products.&nbsp;</b><br><br>Ask for detail information, product specification and prices via email and chat support, drop your requirements, and message our reprehensive connect in 24 hours with details information! We believe in customer satisfaction in all aspects. Our team is committed to providing high-quality laboratory equipment at attractive prices!&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>', 'Metallurgical Microscope', 'Metallurgical Microscope manufacturers, suppliers and exporters in India. Atico leading Lab Microscope and accessories suppliers at best prices! Ask details', 'Metallurgical Microscope Manufacturers and Suppliers in India', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:30', '2022-05-13 16:40:03', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
(161, 'Spectrophotometer', '145', NULL, NULL, 0, 'Spectrophotometer', NULL, '448915Spectrophotometer.jpg', 'spectrophotometer', 'A range of Spectrophotometer is available at Atico house based on high quality and best price. We are always ahead in order to meet the product demand.\nAtico export is <strong>Spectrophotometer Manufacturer and Supplier</strong> in the global market. We always consider the customer satisfaction. We do not compromise with quality, that is why our clients rage is rising day by day in international market.\nWe have started our business in 1954 and gradually our products began to meet the international standards. To get any product you have to call us or send your specifications via email. We will send you the further information on your mail id as soon as possible.', 'Spectrophotometer', 'Spectrophotometer manufacturers, supplier and exporters in India. Get ISO certified laboratory equipment contact us for quote', 'Spectrophotometer Manufacturers, Supplier and Exporter In India', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:30', '2019-11-06 19:16:44', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
