(163, 'Beakers', '379', NULL, NULL, 0, 'Beakers', NULL, '528234SB45964-main-530Wx530H.jpg', 'beakers', '<h2>India\'s Best&nbsp;Beakers Manufacturer, Supplier, and Exporter</h2><div><br></div><div>We at Atico Lab Export emerged in designing and developing beakers for different laboratories of schools, colleges, research institutes, and healthcare applications. Our list of <b><a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/category/laboratory-glassware\" title=\"\" target=\"\">Laboratory Glassware</a></b> Beakers is manufactured in different sizes and shapes. such as Conical Beaker, Beaker, Low Form -With spout Capacity, Beakers, Squat Form:-With spout Capacity 100ml 250ml, etc. Place your order through an Email.<br></div>', 'Beakers', 'Beakers manufacturers, supplier and exporters in India. Get ISO certified laboratory equipment contact us for quote', 'Beakers Manufacturers, Supplier and Exporter In India', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:30', '2021-03-04 18:17:02', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
(164, 'Burette', '379', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Burette', NULL, '660822images (1).jpg', 'burette', '<h2>Burette Manufacturer, Supplier &amp; Exporter</h2><div bis_skin_checked=\"1\"><br></div><div bis_skin_checked=\"1\">As a leading Burette manufacturer and supplier, we take pride in delivering products that exceed expectations. Our commitment to quality, accuracy, and innovation sets us apart in the market. With years of expertise and customer trust behind us, we\'ve become the go-to choice for professionals seeking precision instruments.<br></div><div bis_skin_checked=\"1\">Our Burette ensures accurate and reliable results every time. Its high-quality manufacturing and design make it an essential tool for scientists, chemists, and researchers seeking the utmost precision in their experiments. Whether you\'re titrating solutions, measuring precise volumes, or conducting critical analyses, our Burette is your ultimate companion for achieving unparalleled outcomes.<br></div><div bis_skin_checked=\"1\"><br></div>', 'Burette', 'Burette manufacturers, supplier and exporters in India. Get ISO certified laboratory equipment contact us for quote', 'Burette Manufacturers, Supplier and Exporter In India', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:30', '2024-01-11 17:15:01', NULL, NULL, 2, NULL),
