(182, 'Automobile & Thermodynamics Engineering Models', '131', 566, 570, NULL, 'Automobile and Thermodynamics Engineering Models', NULL, '5842842 stroke petrol engine-500x500.jpg', 'automobile-thermodynamics-engineering-models', '<b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\" calibri\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:=\"\" minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa\"=\"\"><h2>Automobile\nand Thermodynamics Engineering Models Manufacturers, Supplier &amp; Exporters</h2></span></b><br><div><br></div><div>A hub of Automobile &amp; Thermodynamics Engineering Models, We are manufacturer and supplier of Automobile &amp; Thermodynamics Engineering Models. We provide Air Compressor Study, Infrared Thermometer, Thermocouple, Lever Safety Valve, and many more. Every Equipment details are mentioned below; you can easily check the specification as per your requirement.\n\nmore information about <a href=\"https://www.aticoexport.com/product_category/technical-educational-equipment\" title=\"\" target=\"\">Technical Educational Equipment</a>. visit at main page of Technical Educational Equipment</div>', 'Automobile and Thermodynamics Engineering Models', 'We are Manufacturer, Supplier and Exporter of Automobile and Thermodynamics Engineering Models. Checkout the product’s specification on our website.', 'Automobile and Thermodynamics Engineering Models Manufacturer', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:31', '2021-11-11 13:18:28', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
(183, 'Chemistry Lab Safety Equipments', '347', 569, NULL, NULL, 'Chemistry Lab Equipment', NULL, '786267school-chemistry-lab-equipment-500x500.jpg', 'chemistry-lab-safety-equipments', '<div>A chemistry laboratory is often described as a center for the discovery and broader learning of chemistry formulations. However, it poses several risks during experiments due to dangerous chemical involvement and fire flames. Hence, safety becomes paramount when you have to deal with these hazardous chemicals during practical experimentation in a chemistry laboratory.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>We are the largest chemistry lab safety equipment manufacturer, supplier, and exporter in India serving the scientific industry worldwide. Chemistry laboratory safety equipment provided by Atico Scientific is of paramount importance in preventing accidents and chemical hazards, as we are well aware of the fact that safety comes first.</div><div><br></div><div>Atico Scientific is a trusted name in <a href=\"https://aticoscientific.com/category/laboratory-instruments\" title=\"\" target=\"\">laboratory equipment</a>, providing a comprehensive range of chemistry lab safety products to help institutions and industries maintain a safe and efficient working environment. We as a leading and reliable chemistry laboratory equipment manufacturer and supplier, complement all the safety needs of a chemical laboratory making it a safe experimenting hub for students and professionals.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><h2>Importance of Chemistry Lab Safety Equipment by a Trusted Manufacturing Company</h2><div>Safety equipment from Atico Scientific enables laboratories to guarantee the safety and security of the research laboratory and all professionals and students involved. We ensure safe experimentation through a wide range of safety equipment for chemistry laboratories:</div><div><br></div><div>1) Chemical Splash Proof Glasses</div><div>2) Mask Goggles</div><div>3) Lab Coats and Aprons</div><div>4) Gloves (Rubber, Polythene)</div><div>5) Wooden cork stopper</div><div>6) Fume hoods</div><div>7) Fire extinguishers</div><div>8) Chemical storage cabinets</div><div><br></div><div>Our durable and quality product range supports optimal performance without compromising the safety of the students. Quality-certified products by Atico Scientific cater to safety solutions that would precisely be what a laboratory would require in schools, colleges, and research centers.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><h2>Making a Safe Chemistry Laboratory in Collaboration with Atico Scientific&nbsp;</h2><div>This will involve thoughtful designing, safety rules, and necessary safety equipment to establish a perfectly safe lab. Atico Scientific makes the work easier by providing complete end-to-end support covering the selection of all tools that need to be installed along with comprehensive support in setting it up in the laboratory.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>For educational institutes, Atico Scientific ensures that the students learn safely without the risks of accidents and industrial professionals innovate without compromising security. With the mantra of quality, innovation, and customer satisfaction, Atico Scientific has been a great hand to laboratories all over the world.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Atico Scientific produces countless varieties of laboratory safety equipment tailored to the industry that enables laboratories to work with confidence and peace of mind.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Go for a safer, smarter, and more secure laboratory experience with Atico Scientific.</div>', 'Chemistry Lab Equipment', 'Find reliable chemistry lab safety equipment from a leading manufacturer and supplier. We offer a wide range of products for schools, colleges, and research labs', 'Chemistry Lab Safety Equipments Manufacturer and Supplier in India - Atico Scientific', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:31', '2025-02-10 08:29:09', NULL, NULL, 2, NULL),
(184, 'Chemistry Equipments', '347', 569, 567, NULL, 'Chemistry Equipments', NULL, '734889chemistry-lab-equipment-500x500.jpg', 'chemistry-equipments', '<h2>Manufacturer, Supplier, and Exporter of&nbsp;Chemistry Equipments</h2><br>', 'Chemistry Equipments', 'We are Manufacturer, Supplier and Exporter of Educational lab Equipments and Chemistry Equipments. We supply a huge range of chemistry lab apparatus across the world.', 'Chemistry and Educational Equipments Manufacturer, Supplier and Exporter', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:31', '2021-11-11 13:42:21', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
