(198, 'Laboratory Instruments', '347', 569, 571, NULL, 'Laboratory Instruments', NULL, '501938Geotechnical-engineering-lab-equipment.jpg', 'laboratory-instruments', '<div>Laboratories lay a very strong foundation for scientific development. That is where the real magic happens when discovering science, innovation, and much more. Demand for laboratory instrumentation never have been so high among academic institutions, research institute laboratories, and industrial testing laboratories.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>That is why Atico Scientific, aims to be one of the best manufacturing, supplying, and exporting companies by providing high-quality laboratory instruments. Atico Scientific and its role in the global market for laboratory equipment is described by its focus on modern technology and the highly experienced engineering professionals that make the manufacturing process possible.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><h2>Atico Scientific: your Laboratory Instruments Partner&nbsp;</h2><div>Atico Scientific is more than a name in laboratory equipment manufacturing, instead, it\'s a whole experience of reliability, quality, and innovation in supplying laboratory instruments. Be it a new lab setup, a laboratory replacing aged equipment, or expanding existing research capabilities, one has a one-stop solution to meet such objectives fast and within budget by partnering with Atico Scientific.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>The product range at Atico Scientific ranges from the very basic educational type of laboratory instruments to very highly advanced scientific instruments in chemistry, biology, material science, engineering, and research laboratories. Based on the unique requirements of these modern laboratories the very reliable laboratory instrument manufacturer and supplier provide tailored solutions to meet those individual needs.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>We manufacture premium quality laboratory instruments that match the exact requirements of the client’s obje