21:32', '2025-02-10 09:49:38', NULL, NULL, 2, NULL),
(199, 'Thermodynamics Lab', '131', 566, NULL, 0, 'Thermodynamics Lab', NULL, '991057separating-and-throttling-calorimeter-500x500.jpg', 'thermodynamics-lab', '<h2>Thermodynamics Lab Equipment</h2><div><br></div>Atico Lab Export is a leading <b>Thermodynamics Lab Equipment Manufacturer, Supplier and Exporter in India </b>and worldwide. We are leading our production with all types of instruments to learn the fundamentals of Thermodynamics. We are available to serve the best quality. We have new ideas to manufacture the product based on the latest technology. All products will be delivered within a short period to the customer. We are the supplier of the most trusted and ultimate<b> thermodynamics lab equipment&nbsp;</b>brand. If there is any issue regarding the consignments, then we give the facility of warranty so that you can change your product to the new one without any concerns.<br><br><h2><h3>Thermodynamics Lab Equipment&nbsp;</h3><br></h2>We offer the top-quality&nbsp;<b><a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/category/mechanical-engineering\" title=\"mechanical engineering lab equipment manufacturers\" target=\"\">mechanical&nbsp;engineering lab equipments</a></b> products which are highly recommended for the interested clients. For any queries about products or post-purchase services, you can reach us on email or contact numbers provided on the website. Now you can set up a fully functional lab for your schools, universities, research centres or industries with Atico Lab Export House in India and Worldwide.&nbsp;<div><br></div><div>Ask for details via email and chat support, drop your requirements, and message our reprehensive connect in 24 hours with details information! We believe in customer satisfaction in all aspects. Our team is committed to providing high-quality laboratory equipment at attractive prices!<br></div>', 'Thermodynamics Lab', 'Thermodynamics lab manufacturers, supplier and exporters in India. Get ISO certified laboratory equipment contact us for quote', 'Thermodynamics Lab Manufacturers, Supplier and Exporter In India', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:32', '2022-05-13 16:27:57', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
(200, 'Basins And Crucibles', '347', 569, 567, NULL, 'Basins And Crucibles', NULL, '246886crucible-lids-basins-and-porcelain-ware-500x500.jpg', 'basins-and-crucibles', '<div>Laboratory apparatus as small as a cup size is highly essential for numerous applications that include chemical analysis and testing, such as metal refinement and much more, with the capacity to withstand a high-temperature range. With decades of experience as Basins and Crucibles manufacturers, suppliers, and exporters, Atico Scientific has emerged as a premium name.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Every product provided by us promises durability, precision, and functionality. For any experiment you are conducting, whether a routine or industrial process, our products will give you a consistent output.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><h2>Why Basins and Crucibles Are Required in a Laboratory?</h2><div>Basins and crucibles are useful tools that serve numerous purposes in a laboratory.&nbsp;</div><div>1) Heating and Melting</div><div>2) Evaporation</div><div>3) Chemical Reactions</div><div>4) Testing of Material Properties</div><div><br></div><div>The accuracy and reliability of this kind of equipment are extremely important to achieve accurate outcomes both in laboratory and industrial settings. That’s why Atico Scientific is rated as one of the leading basin and crucible suppliers and exporters in India and across the world, as we provide high-quality basins and crucibles.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><h2>Why Choose Atico Scientific as Your Trusted Partner?</h2><div>Atico Scientific manufactures basins and crucibles using the best quality material. Porcelain, graphite, quartz, and metal alloys are used to withstand extreme temperature conditions. Every product is made with precision and care so that size, shape, and performance are uniform.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>We are a reliable basins and crucibles exporter, and the quality of our products has placed us high in the global market. We export our products across the world to fulfill the demands of all types of laboratories. We provide tailored solutions in basins and crucibles to meet the diversified applications of a laboratory ensuring optimal performance.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Range of Basins and Crucibles by Atico Scientific&nbsp;</div><div><b>Porcelain Basins</b></div><div>1) Evaporation Basins</div><div>2) Glazed and Unglazed Basins</div><div>3) Acid Resistant Basins</div><div><br></div><div><b>Crucibles</b></div><div>1) High-Temperature Porcelain Crucibles</div><div>2) Graphite Crucibles</div><div>3) Quartz Crucibles</div><div>4) Platinum Crucibles</div><div>5) Metal Crucibles (Stainless steel Crucibles)</div><div><br></div><div><b>Accessories</b></div><div>1) Crucible tongs</div><div>2) Crucible stations</div><div>3) Basins and Crucible Covers and Lids</div><div><br></div><div>These basins and crucibles are used for a variety of purposes in research and industries. Highly used in chemistry, biology, materials science, research laboratories, and environmental testing.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div><b>Why Do Clients Choose Us?</b></div><div>Atico Scientific provides a wide variety of basins and crucibles to meet the specific needs of any laboratory, regardless of size or age of the laboratory. Atico Scientific is dedicated to providing the best solutions across scientific and industrial realms that drive success and excellence in experiments.</div>', 'Basins And Crucibles', 'Leading Basins and Crucibles manufacturer, supplier & exporter in India. High-quality lab supplies for schools, colleges, and industries.', 'Basins And Crucibles Manufacturer, Supplier and Exporter In India', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:32', '2025-02-10 10:01:45', NULL, NULL, 2, NULL),
