(286, 'Microscope Accessories', '153', NULL, NULL, 0, 'Microscope Accessories', NULL, '866676download (3).jpg', 'microscope-accessories', '<p><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\" calibri\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:=\"\" minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa\"=\"\"></span></b></p><h2><b>Microscope\nAccessories Manufacturers, Suppliers, and Exporters</b></h2><p></p><p>We are <strong>manufacturer and supplier of Microscope Accessories</strong>. As Atico is a trusted brand in the international market, we corner the market based on our best quality. We offer superior quality, high-tech tool, and technology standards, less maintenance, and other services.<br></p> \n<p>Clients, who once get connected with us they never get disappointed for their required best quality <strong><a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/\" title=\"\" target=\"\"> School Science Lab Supplies</a>.</strong> </p>\n<p>You can easily get your product by sending us an email in which you have mentioned the proper specifications as required.</p>', 'Microscope Accessories', 'Avail the fantastic range of Microscope Accessories Manufacturers, Suppliers and Exporters and other School Science Lab Supplies at Atico Lab Export.', 'Microscope Accessories Manufacturers, Suppliers and Exporters', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:35', '2021-01-06 14:17:17', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
(287, 'Laboratory Microscopes ', '153', NULL, NULL, 0, 'Laboratory Microscopes', NULL, '223628download (1).jpg', 'laboratory-microscopes', 'We are manufacturer and supplier of <strong>Laboratory Microscope</strong>. You are invited to call us on Facebook, Twitter as well as Google+.\nWe supply the products as per the latest technological advancements and up to the expectations.\nOur ethical business policies grasp the market and provide individual client specified requirements. We have achieved success based on our product’s advancement. All varieties of <strong><a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/category/microscopes\" title=\"\" target=\"\">Lab Microscopes</a></strong> are available in Atico House.', 'Laboratory Microscopes', 'Atico design and manufacture Laboratory Microscope with international quality standards. Our Supplier and Exporter supply all the stock in global science market.', 'Laboratory Microscopes Manufacturers, Suppliers and Exporters', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:36', '2020-12-22 15:26:33', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
(288, 'Laboratory Centrifuges', '0', NULL, NULL, 0, 'Laboratory Centrifuges', NULL, '965212cen.jpg', 'laboratory-centrifuges', 'If you want to buy Lab Centrifuge and looking for <strong>Lab Centrifuge Manufacturer</strong>, who can provide the best quality of Lab Centrifuge. Then you have reached the right place. Atico Export is one the best <strong>Lab Centrifuge Manufacturer</strong> in Ambala. We provide our service as <strong>Lab Centrifuge Supplier</strong>&nbsp;all over the world. For more information, you can check on this page.', 'Laboratory Centrifuges', 'Laboratory centrifuges manufacturers, supplier and exporters in India. Get ISO certified laboratory equipment contact us for quote', 'Laboratory Centrifuges Prices, Manufacturer and Supplier In India', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:36', '2019-10-14 18:56:00', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
