(290, 'Measurement Meters', '349', NULL, NULL, 0, 'Measurement Meters', NULL, '97641651C7CWJ7sOL._SX466_.jpg', 'measurement-meters', '<h2>Manufacturer, Supplier, and Exporter of Measurement Meters for Research or Physics Labs</h2><div><br></div><div>Atico Export provides Measuring instruments which are a device for measuring a physical quantity, are <a href=\"https://aticolabexport.com/category/physics-lab-equipments\" title=\"\" target=\"\"><b>useful tools in the physical sciences</b></a>, quality assurance, and engineering purpose. They measure and compare the activity of physical objects of the real-world.&nbsp; They can be simple, like rulers, or complex.\n\nWe manufacturer a nephelometer in our firm that is used for measuring the concentration of suspended particulates in a liquid or gas colloid. In other words, we can say that the nephelometer measures suspended particulates by employing a light beam and a light detector set to one of the source beams. We build these measurement devices in special order also for school, colleges, or industrial demands and deliver the quality product in the provided time frame. Our experienced and well-trained professionals export all kind of laboratory purpose equipment and instrument all over the world.\n<div class=\"ginger-module-correctionBubble-onboarding\">\n<div class=\"ginger-module-correctionBubble-onboarding-bubble ginger-module-correctionBubble-onboarding-top\">To approve a single suggestion, mouse over it and click \"✔\"</div>\n<div class=\"ginger-module-correctionBubble-onboarding-bubble ginger-module-correctionBubble-onboarding-bottom\">Click the bubble to approve all of its suggestions.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ginger-module-correctionBubble\" style=\"padding: 0px; top: 122.868px; left: 127.969px; display: none;\" contenteditable=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ginger-module-correctionBubble-container ginger-module-correctionBubble-container-loggedout\">\n<div class=\"ginger-module-correctionBubble-login\">Log in</div>\n<div class=\"ginger-module-correctionBubble-body\">to use Ginger</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ginger-module-correctionBubble-container ginger-module-correctionBubble-container-loggedin\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<div class=\"ginger-module-correctionBubble-limited\">Limited mode</div>\n<div class=\"ginger-module-correctionBubble-body\">nephelometer</div>\n<a class=\"ginger-module-correctionBubble-close\" title=\"Ignore mistake\">×</a></div>\n</div></div>', 'Measurement Meters', 'We are Manufacturer, Supplier and Exporter of Measurement Meters used in educational or engineering laboratories of school, college or universities.', 'Measurement Meters Manufacturer, Supplier and Exporter', 1, '2019-09-12 09:21:36', '2021-01-07 13:05:39', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL),
