(568, 'Engineering Lab Equipment', '0', NULL, NULL, 0, 'Engineering Lab Equipment, civil engineering lab equipment, chemical lab equipment', NULL, '288151Engineering Lab Equipment Manufacturer.jpg', 'engineering-lab-equipment', '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-8aa65224-7fff-5ece-ebd3-54b3ee98a266\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">Engineering disciplines combine scientific concepts with application-oriented research to produce systems and processes that provide new learning methods. Engineering is vital to effective industrial innovation because of this integration.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">An Engineer doesn\'t just sit around and wait for things to happen; they take action. Engineering graduates impact the world unlike any other, thanks to their invention, creativity, and abundance of knowledge. The world is changing, and engineers are liable for a great deal of it.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">If the Engineering discipline is that important, you also need the highest quality possible equipment for an engineering lab. For that, you also need to find the best engineering lab equipment manufacturer and exporter.&nbsp;</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><b>Atico India</b>&nbsp;is a renowned name when it comes to the advanced Engineering lab equipment manufacturer and supplier in India. Our Engineering Equipment production business creates conventional and customized Engineering Lab Equipment for civil, mechanical, and chemical engineering. Using high-quality raw materials, our expert team of manufacturers and exporters strives to deliver complete customer satisfaction.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><br></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: large; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700; text-align: left;\">For the details Information you can connect with us via chat, email “</span><a href=\"mailto:sales@aticolabexport.com\" title=\"\" target=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(73, 133, 184); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: none; box-shadow: none; line-height: inherit; font-size: large; transition-duration: 0.3s; font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700; text-align: left;\">sales@aticoindia.com&nbsp;<span class=\"fa fa-arrow-right\" style=\"font-style: inherit; speak: none;\"></span></a><span style=\"font-size: large; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700; text-align: left;\">” and customer support phone number&nbsp;</span><a href=\"tel:+919896793832\" title=\"\" target=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(73, 133, 184); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: none; box-shadow: none; line-height: inherit; font-size: large; transition-duration: 0.3s; font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700; text-align: left;\">“+91-9696793832”</a><br></span></p><br><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 700;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">Civil Engineering Lab Equipment Manufacturer</span></h2><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">Civil Engineering is a professional engineering major that focuses on the design, development, and management of naturally occurring and artificial environments such as roads, buildings, bridges, dams, pipelines, airports, and trains.&nbsp;</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">There are numerous job prospects in civil engineering. As a Civil Engineer, you can pursue a variety of professional and career prospects. There are several chances in the public sector as well. If you are determined and passionate when it comes to your work, you can have a successful career.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">Without civil engineers, there would be no contemporary society. Roads, airports, train stations, and other modes of transportation all require civil engineers to build. Professional civil engineering abilities are also necessary for the building of our services, which include water, power, phone, and internet.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">Civil engineers are among the most critical engineers in our civilization. Almost every element of life, from shopping to showering, is dependent on a construction project that would not be possible without a civil engineer. But it all starts with education. It would be best if you went deeply into the practical notion in order to build exceptional constructions. Best practices lead to even better outcomes. As a result, the equipment used in civil engineering labs should be error-free and of superior quality. If you are seeking the best civil engineering lab equipment manufacturer and exporter, then you can count on ATICO India.&nbsp;</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">When it comes to innovative Engineering lab equipment manufacturers and suppliers in India, ATICO India is a well-known name. Our Engineering Equipment manufacturing firm offers standard and customized Engineering Lab Equipment for civil, mechanical, and chemical engineering. We export the highest quality equipment around the globe, which makes us the best engineering lab equipment exporter.</span></p><br><h2 style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 700;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><b>Mechanical Engineering Lab Equipment manufacturer and supplier</b></span></h2><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">Archimedes said, \"Give me a place to stand, and I will move the earth.\" This statement must have clarified the importance of Mechanical Engineering.&nbsp;</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">Mechanical engineering is a major of engineering that focuses on the design, analysis, construction, and maintenance of mechanical systems using materials science, engineering physics, and mathematics. It is one of the earliest and most varied engineering fields.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">Mechanical engineering is responsible for the development of engines, generators, elevators, and even air conditioning. Even if we aren\'t aware of it, we probably use something mechanically engineered on a daily basis.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">Mechanical engineering is employed in a variety of items, including automobiles, planes, and refrigerators. It allows you to efficiently do a variety of daily duties by introducing beneficial technology to our contemporary culture. Many of the technologies we use on a daily basis would not be conceivable without them, making it one of the most vital disciplines of engineering.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">ATICO India, established in Ambala, has dominated the market since 1954. We are a well-known and trustworthy supplier of Mechanical Engineering laboratory equipment. Our ISO-certified company in India manufactures, supplies, and exports engineering laboratory instruments. Our products are precise and accurate in every aspect of the Engineering Lab Industry. It\'s our company\'s principles and solid consumer base that makes us the most reliable Engineering lab equipment manufacturer and supplier.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 700;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><b>Chemical Engineering Lab Equipment Exporter</b></span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">Chemical Engineering is a discipline that deals with the operation and design of chemical plants, as well as ways for improving production. Chemical Engineering encompasses not only chemistry and chemicals but also physics, mathematics, biology, and economics in order to precisely use, create, produce, and transmit material and energy.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">Chemical engineering leads to material and energy transformation and production, but it all starts with a laboratory experiment. As a result, the tools and equipment utilized there should be faultless and of the highest quality. Traditional methods were time-consuming and dangerous, necessitating the use of laboratory equipment. If you\'re looking for the best engineering laboratory equipment supplier in India for Chemical Engineering, look no further. ATICO India is again the phenomenal Chemical Engineering Lab Equipment Manufacturer and Exporter you were looking for.&nbsp;</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\">ATICO India is a global leader in the manufacturing, distributing, and exporting of Engineering Laboratory Equipment. To our loyal customers, we provide an unrivalled blend of breakthrough technologies, purchasing convenience, and comprehensive services. We are, without a doubt, the world\'s unchallenged leader in the production of high-performance Engineering and other laboratory equipment. Our technical team is committed to exceeding our clients\' expectations and pushing for excellence in all aspects of the company. All these qualities make us the leading engineering lab equipment manufacturer and supplier.</span></p></span>', 'Engineering Lab Equipment, civil engineering lab equipment, chemical lab equipment', 'Engineering lab equipment leading manufacturer, supplier & exporters in India. Products meet international standards and quality not compromised.', 'Engineering Lab Equipment Manufacturers & Suppliers In India', 1, NULL, '2024-05-15 11:24:59', NULL, NULL, 2, NULL),
(569, 'School Science Lab Equipment Manufacturer', '0', NULL, NULL, 0, 'School Science Lab Equipment Manufacturer', NULL, '986888school-science-lab-equipment-manufacturers.jpg', 'school-science-lab-equipment', '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-cb550ca8-7fff-05c4-edca-c8eec2ea11ac\"><h2 style=\"line-height:1.3800000000000001;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><font color=\"#0e101a\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"5\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">School Science Lab Equipment Manufacturer in India</span></font></span></h2><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.3800000000000001;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><br></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.3800000000000001;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"><font size=\"4\">Atico India is the leading and most reliable School science lab equipment manufacturer in India. Our goods are of extremely high-quality and are used by the customers worldwide. We offer a wide range of scientific lab instruments manufactured in our well-equipped manufacturing facility in Ambala, Haryana. We have the perfect blend of innovative technology and highly skilled personnel, allowing Atico India to create the industry\'s most basic scientific workplace instrum