(570, 'TVET Lab Equipment manufacturers', '0', NULL, NULL, 0, 'TVET Lab Equipment manufacturers', NULL, '283959912308fluidized-bed-dryer-apparatus-img.jpg', 'tvet-lab-equipment', '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-53ad84a4-7fff-30f4-5bea-42dda76451df\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.3800000000000001;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(14,=\"\" 16,=\"\" 26);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" transparent;=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" normal;=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" baseline;=\"\" white-space:=\"\" pre-wrap;\"=\"\"></span></p><h2 style=\"\"><b>Technical Educational Equipments Manufacturer, Supplier &amp; Exporter</b><br></h2><div bis_skin_checked=\"1\"><br></div><div bis_skin_checked=\"1\">Atico India is the leading manufacturer and supplier of <b><a href=\"https://www.aticoindia.com/category/tvet-lab-equipment\" title=\"\" target=\"\">TVET lab equipments</a> in India</b>. we understand the importance of equipping learners with the tools they need to develop practical skills and gain real-world experience. We are the supplier and manufacturer of an immense collection of Technical Lab Instruments particularly used in engineering training. Our head office is located in Ambala Cantt, Haryana, India. In the industry of producing science lab equipment, Atico India is a well-known brand name. We offer a wide range of products related to science, technology, and engineering.<br></div><div bis_skin_checked=\"1\"><br></div><div bis_skin_checked=\"1\">From engineering and electronics to automotive and culinary arts, our diverse range of <b>TVET-technical and vocational educational equipment</b> caters to a wide array of vocational training needs. We offer a comprehensive selection of training systems, simulators, apparatus, and tools that replicate industry-standard environments, enabling students to bridge the gap between theory and practice.<br></div><div bis_skin_checked=\"1\"><br></div><div bis_skin_checked=\"1\"><br></div><div bis_skin_checked=\"1\"><br></div><div bis_skin_checked=\"1\"><b><br></b></div><div bis_skin_checked=\"1\"><br></div><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.3800000000000001;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p></span>', 'TVET Lab Equipment manufacturers', 'TVET Lab Equipments manufactruer and supplier, TVET Lab Equipments exporter, Technical educational Equipment Supplier in India. Contact us for bulk order.', 'TVET Lab Equipment Manufacturer and Suppliers in India', 1, '2021-09-20 12:37:05', '2023-06-23 18:42:03', NULL, 1, 2, NULL),
