(573, 'Laboratory Plasticware', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Laboratory Plasticware', NULL, '188478laboratory-plasticware-manufacturer.png', 'laboratory-plasticware', '<div>Atico India is recognized as the most dependable manufacturer of laboratory plasticware in India, and it is renowned for delivering top-notch quality at competitive prices. Laboratory Plasticware refers to the collection of tools or equipment utilized in laboratories to heat chemicals at moderate temperatures and conduct vigorous chemical reactions.</div><div><br></div><div>Plastic labware offers several benefits: it is lightweight, reusable, eco-friendly, and can be sterilized through autoclaving. Additionally, plastic labware is recyclable, can be disposed of after use, and is non-breakable, flexible, and more economical than glassware.</div><div><br></div><div>Our network of authorized distributors ensures that our Laboratory Plasticware reaches customers across the country. Our extensive range of lab plasticware includes stackable beakers, beaker sets, handled plastic beakers, reagent bottles, wash bottles, carboys, burettes, measuring cylinders, volumetric flasks, conical flasks, funnels, funnel holders, Pasteur pipettes, pipette pumps, pipette stands, test tube stands, spatulas, and stirring rods.</div>', 'Laboratory Plasticware', 'Laboratory Plasticware Manufacturer, Supplier. Atico India is leading Laboratory Plasticware Manufacturer suppliers across the world, Contact us now for bulk order.', 'Laboratory Plasticware Manufacturer Manufacturer, Suppliers and Exporter - Atico India', 1, '2024-06-03 13:18:25', '2024-06-03 13:18:25', NULL, 2, NULL, NULL);
